Package: libcreativity0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Economic creativity and piracy simulator (shared library)
 Creativity is an economics agent-based model that simulates the creative process,
 including creation, sales, and piracy of creative works.
 .
 This package contains the base shared library needed for all creativity tools.

